The Chronicle Nqobile Tshili, Chronicle Reporter AILING Zapu president and liberation war stalwart Dr Dumiso Dabengwa has been flown to India for specialised treatment of a reported liver disease, his party has confirmed. Dr Dabengwa spent some time in South Africa last December receiving treatment for the same ailment. In a statement on Wednesday, Zapu national spokesperson Mr Iphithule Maphosa said Dr Dabengwa has been flown to India to get specialised treatment. More details to followâ€¦